HEADWORD: Eventful
<hw>E*vent"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>a.</pos> <def>Full of, or rich in,
events or incidents; <as>as, an <ex>eventful</ex> journey; an
<ex>eventful</ex> period of history; an <ex>eventful</ex> period of
life.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

